          "plain_text": "The day passes in a flash and I’m feeling pretty tired. Fred runs off at 5pm and I head home. We are going to go to visit Josh Hartford at Misha’s house after dinner. It’s Friday night and we don’t feel like cooking. We flex a Bolt Food voucher and devour two curries that even while being medium still pack quite a punch.",
